Grid System:
    .row -- ***** Takes the whole space of one row  *****
            make columns in a row and no space left and right to the screen,
            otherwise, even inside the .container-fluid, there will
            be spaces beside columns

BackGround:
    jumbotron -- large screen

Container:
    .container -- has space on the left and right
    .container-fluid -- has no space, full screen

Text:
    .text-right
    .text-center
    .text-uppercase
    .text-lowercase

Table:
    .table -- full line table
    .table-striped -- change rows to grey and white
    .table-condensed -- remove padding and margin
    .table-hover -- add hover effects
    .table-bordered -- add border to the table

Image:
    .center-block -- make the image center
    .thumbnail -- add frame to the image
    .img-circle -- make the image circle
    .img-responsive -- make the image responsive
    .img-thumbnail -- works as .thumbnail + .img-responsive

Button:
    .btn -- make as a bootstrap button
    .btn-default -- add hover to .btn
    .btn-primary -- add color to button
    .btn-link -- make button look like a link
    .btn-lg/md/sm/xs -- change the button size
    .btn-block -- full screen width button
    .disabled -- make disabled
    .btn-group -- make buttons as a group with padding and margin removed
    .btn-group-vertical -- make the button group vertical
    .btn-group-justified -- justified to the parents

    .dropdown-toggle -- toggle dropdown <ul> list, make button property as data-toggle="dropdown"
    .dropdown-menu -- make ul work with dropdown trigger button
    .divider -- add to <li>'s class, make a line between li in the drop down menu
    .dropdown-header -- make <li> as a header

    .dropdown-menu-right -- make the dropdown <ul> appear from right of the screen
    .dropup -- make the <ul> appear on the top of the trigger button not bottom
